object.name: text
object.text: Ange? Is that you? What happened to you? Why are you doing this to us?

object.name: text
object.text: Amelia?! ... I'm too late. You're cursed now. I've failed as your sister...I'm so sorry.

object.name: text
object.text: Cursed? What curse?! We were all so happy living together-- How can it be a curse?

object.name: text
object.text: The demon curse on this land since our Kingdom's beginning! We've already lost too many girls like you!

object.name: text
object.text: If you don't want to be like us, why don't you leave us alone? Why don't you go somewhere else?!

object.name: text
object.text:
We have nowhere else. We have no choice!
Amelia, I love you. God rest your soul!
